    "name": "堕天使复仇",
    "steam_appid": 3273740,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《堕天使复仇》是一款类Rogue地城探索动作游戏，结合近身和远程作战的玩法，更融入灵异主题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身冤屈落魄的反叛天使亚巴顿，踏上复仇之路，骑着摩托驶入上帝遗弃的废土，追杀各路邪魔鬼怪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/3270ee2d6dbc6a5add622a2d75b90ee7.poster.avif?t=1763136040\" width=800 height=482 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/3270ee2d6dbc6a5add622a2d75b90ee7.webm?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/3270ee2d6dbc6a5add622a2d75b90ee7.mp4?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追杀途中不断增强自身实力，壮大武器装备，获得来自异界的支持，夺回理应属于你的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《堕天使复仇》每次追杀的关卡都是程序生成，你要闯过这些关卡，才能找到污染这片土地的魔鬼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一局都可以在长剑、枪支和魔法护符之间选一件装备。追杀期间，异界的守护神还会随机赋予你法咒和能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/c9697763e6f4d4fad9c5d9d2f11114a2.poster.avif?t=1763136040\" width=800 height=482 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/c9697763e6f4d4fad9c5d9d2f11114a2.webm?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/c9697763e6f4d4fad9c5d9d2f11114a2.mp4?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一局完成之后，还能获得永久有效的奖励，供你未来使用。即便没能完成一局游戏，你也会获得一些资源，供你在路边酒馆增强实力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >给你的武器和座驾升级，注入深渊墨水，获得力量纹身。不要忘了去找那个神秘的酒保，买些路上喝的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/0edc44b75396fec235aceff2c67be0d8.poster.avif?t=1763136040\" width=800 height=482 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/0edc44b75396fec235aceff2c67be0d8.webm?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/0edc44b75396fec235aceff2c67be0d8.mp4?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >勇闯神弃之地，屠杀程序生成的魔王，才能获得重要的钥匙，进入地狱深处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭破地狱封印之后，你就会在追杀途中遇到新的敌人，遭遇新的事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地狱每一层都有一个独一无二的魔王，击杀之后才能继续深入。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/ed0f520be0fbdfa717cc7163007ad9d0.poster.avif?t=1763136040\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/ed0f520be0fbdfa717cc7163007ad9d0.webm?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/ed0f520be0fbdfa717cc7163007ad9d0.mp4?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《堕天使复仇》这款动作游戏虽然注重玩法，但也有一定的设定和剧情元素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将逐步了解亚巴顿如何遭到背叛，帮助他获得清白，拿回他所失去的东西。</p>",
